    "Participants were asked to interact with the robot using natural language instructions and provide feedback on the system's performance.",
    "The evaluation focused on the following aspects:• Usability: Participants rated the ease of interaction with the robot on a scale of 1 to 5.",
    "• Effectiveness: Participants rated the robot's ability to complete tasks accurately and safely on a scale of 1 to 5.",
